{"tid":2089965,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國駐英國大使館反對英國為BNO持有人成為公民鋪路","createTime":"2020-07-02T02:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T02:58:00.000Z","uid":60281,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d3f7e34a44f4e63c47c32d49ffdd41e41ea4510e","tid":2089965,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T02:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國駐英國大使館發言人回應時表示堅決反對，並保留採取相應措施的權利，又說如果英方執意單方面改變有關做法，不僅違背自身立場和承諾，亦違反國際法和國際關係基本準則。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，英方曾與中方互換備忘錄，明確承諾不給予持有BNO的香港中國公民，在英國獲得居留權。全國人大常委會在相關的國籍法中明確指出，所有香港中國同胞，不論是否持有英國屬土公民護照或者BNO，都是中國公民。中方敦促英方客觀公正看待香港特區維護國家安全立法問題，尊重中方立場和關切，不以任何方式干涉香港事務。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535319-20200702.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535319-20200702.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9RA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=4fbcd2f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535319-20200702.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e745fbe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535319-20200702.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"404b6dd95aa3b6197384c0953b57789e40c57739","tid":2089965,"uid":63909,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T02:14:39.000Z","msg":"有無搞錯、關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f586ac5f7a95618d0be8e707f785b8ad0e696be","tid":2089965,"uid":44388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor